Remember the new
developers.google.com is live.

00:08:22.429 --> 00:08:24.470
Go and check it out, and
you can learn about some

00:08:24.470 --> 00:08:26.700
of these great technologies
that we were talking about.

00:08:26.700 --> 00:08:27.455
Thank you so much.

00:08:27.455 --> 00:08:28.300
And thanks again.

